<tr>
	<td class="alt1" width="175" align="center" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><b>drangsuck</b>
<span class="smallfont">
	<br />
	Suspended<br />
	
	
	<br />
	Joined: Jan 2004<br />
	
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I was really excited when LDoN came out. While all the people who liked to raid would be off gearing up, I could do it my way, through consecutive weeks of xping. Not a bad idea overall, coming from SoE right?<br />
<br />
Well, the thing that discouraged me as of recently is seeing POTIME gear being augmented up the yin-yang with LDoN augs.<br />
<br />
The balance would have been there if augs only worked up to a certain point on gear, say non-elemental + <br />
<br />
Now the strong keep getting stronger, and those who thought SoE had devised a clever system to allow those who are not able to fall into the "raid" category to work hard to gear up, have to face the sumber reality that they care not to change things.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
