	<!-- message -->
	<p>You do realize that you can get better gear through LDoN than you can by doing anything else short of elemental planes and raiding, don't you? What makes you think you should be able to get gear as good as those who raid there and Time (no, I don't) have? Why shouldn't those with good gear also be able to improve it through this new system? You CAN gear up better than you could before, so what do you care if Time people can do so as well?</p>
	
	
	
