	<p>I've never done an LDON adventure (yet), but I've certainly benifited from the expansion. I pretty much started on the ass end of the divide too. When I started playing again I was 36, in allmost all Ivy, wielding a SSoM &amp; SWA in a post-PoP world, and nearly broke to boot.  It really doesn't get too much worse than that based on what I've seen, especially weapons wise. Ivy's not that wreched so that carried me a bit further, but my weapons sucked before I stopped, I was busy shopping for a SSoY when I did, as that was the uber-weapon of the day. <br />
