	<p>just being cynical a bit but..<br />
<br />
do you really think the time enabled people would have bothered hitting LDON adventures if they had been unable to augment their own gear ? <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
<br />
Also I dont quite get why augments shouldnt work for Time gear. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
Quite frankly, as it is now, about everything in the game is boring (save the Time level LDON raids where you actually still have a modicum of challenge) farming. <br />
<br />
You can rant as much as you want about how unfair it is for Time geared people to better their gear through LDON, but quite frankly.... <br />
Either youre a raider or youre not. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /> <br />
If youre not, then LDON fuilly augmented gear helps you loads and is enough to carry you through your xp grinds, np. <br />
If youre a raider, then indeed you need all the hp you can get, because of the content youre facing. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /> <br />
<br />
So if youre not a raider, I dont see how the gap matters to you. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /></p>
	
	
	
