	<p>In my left hand, I hold "Risk". In my right hand, I hold "Reward".<br />
<br />
Let me hold these up, so everyone can see. *Dangles Risk*....*Waves Reward*.<br />
<br />
Now, I know these look very similar - that is because they are related. Like the Olsen Twins, but not as weird.<br />
<br />
Anyway. As one grows, so grows the other. If Risk gets 5 apples, then Reward gets 5 tickets to see Celine Dion in Las Vegas! No, wait...that's not it...<br />
<br />
If Risk goes up, so does Reward. If you do not feed poor little Risk, then Reward shall surely starve as well. If you don't want your Reward to look like Calista Flockhart, then beef up that Risk to Rosie O'donnel proportions! It only takes a few weeks of this ultra-fab new diet plan! Join today!<br />
<br />
Oh, you don't have the "time" to devote to proper feed and care of your Risk? Well. We have something here - good for beginners, or people with <b>real lives</b> (/shudder - dirty words).<br />
<br />
*Holds up a shiny new LDoN Expasnion*<br />
<br />
Want to try it out? It's like a raid with training wheels. You can take it around the block - don't go too fast, or try to make any sudden changes in playstyles! Risk and Reward are already taken care of in LDoN. They are given just enough love and discipline to not get too out of shape. Like a pet rock.<br />
<br />
Enjoy!</p>
	
	
	
