	<p>I am sure your time is as important as anyone elses, but is your commitment as high as a raiders?<br />
<br />
The vast majority in elementals/time have given up their 'xp' time to advance the guild - most raiders MUST turn up for raids, its normally a guild policy, i.e. you cannot do what you want, when you want a lot of the time - you are commited to putting your efforts into advancing your guild as a whole to gear up for the next level and break into the new content  each time - surely thats worth more reward then logging in when you feel like and grabbing a quick adventure for 30 mins?<br />
<br />
At least I do.</p>
	
	
	
