	<!-- message -->
	<p>Isn't it about having fun? lol<br />
<br />
I love hanging out in dungeons - it's easy, it's laid back, and it's fun.<br />
<br />
I like raiding. I'm not elemental yet, as I haven't seen RZ get lower than 30% at this point. (Darn those adds! LOL) However, There is no way that I could sink 5 hours a day into raiding. If I did 5 hours raiding a day, I would go crazy and quit. If I did 5 hours LDoN a day, I would go crazy and quit. I just try to mix it up, and do what I feel like doing.<br />
<br />
Are the Haves jealous of the Have not's, or the Havenot's jealous of the Haves?<br />
<br />
I bought the evil Mira's BP, since I didn't picture myself getting a coirnav or askr's BP anytime soon, and I'd rather have Veng3 than the WP on the ornate BP.  Should I still be wearing tae ew since I am not uber enough yet to kill RZ? That's the impression I'm getting. <br />
<br />
I think it's fun to go through and decide exactly which holes to fill in my gear with LDoN stuff, and which to wait till I get higher end stuff from PoP bosses.<br />
<br />
<shrug> Just have fun!</p>
	
	
	
